We updated the SimpleServer.py, which listens for the LabVIEW outputs, to reformat the motor positions to relative format. 
We put (x,y)=(0,0) at bottom left corner of MAPMT (P57). This will greatly reduce the back-and-forth needed to double check motor positions during analysis.

Range (mm): X={0;48}, Y={0;48}
